==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Oversize
<hw>O`ver*size"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To cover with viscid
matter.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>O'ersized</qex> with coagulate gore.</q>
